<div class="bodyText intro">
    <div class="pageTitle">REV issuance for RHOC holders</div>
    <div>In 2017, the RChain Cooperative created RHOC tokens and sponsored a private sale. At the launch of main net, February 25, 2020, there was an issuance of REV at a 1:1 ratio based on a holder’s RHOC balance. REV is the currency of the RChain blockchain. Among other things, REV will allow you to bond a validator’s stake, pay transaction fees, and deploy smart contracts on the new RChain blockchain. If you’re interested in building your own RChain-based dApp, you will need to acquire REV in order to do so.
 </div>
</div>

